descriptionHtml:
Please go here to see any future updates.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=15596

This is just my own personal taste in the way of retexturization for the Forsworn armor. Yes it is another Snow Leopard, but still, I hope someone likes it. (I did not alter the helmet for the outfit, because I believe that you could get a much better selection from [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5865]83Willow\'s mod[/url].)

Hopefully someone will use and/or enjoy this retex, I will be updating for various preferences, and if you have any comments on something that you would like to see changed, feel free to comment and I\'ll see if I have the time to do so.
author: Tier1Dusty
